==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: ink-jet printer
<hw>ink"-jet` printer</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Computers)</fld> <def>A
type of printer used as a peripheral device for computers, in which the
color is applied to the paper by spraying liquid ink onto paper through
tiny orifices in a moving print head, to construct the desired pattern
on the paper by placing one dot or several dots at a time on the
paper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inkle</ent>⟦br⟧
